<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, Novemebr 15 (Xinhua) -- The Blue Nile Sack
Factory at Debre-Zeit town, 40 kms south-east of Addis Ababa, has
managed to increase its annual production from 6 to 13 million
sacks, a report said here today.
</P>
<P>
