<HEADLINE> Chinese Premier Winds Up Visit to Japan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Osaka, November 16 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Premier Li Peng left here
for home this evening after winding up a six-day good-will official
visit to Japan.
