<P>
Kwasniewski said Poland highly valued the role China plays on
the international stage. As Poland also plays its appropriate role
in world affairs, it will benefit both Poland and China to have
good cooperation in international politics, he said.
</P>
<P>
He said that he visited China in 1988 as the minister of youths
and sports of the former government. He made a private visit to
China in 1989. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
